    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Assist Steps</title>
        <para>Driver fold down assist steps are located each side of the body on the lower cowl assembly to assist in
            accessing the windshield or wipers for cleaning, servicing or adjustment. Grab handles are also installed
            each side of the bus exterior to assist in accessing the windshield area and wiper assemblies.
        </para>
